q_ch: 主仓库和辅助仓库中，哪个仓库的Cotton Fabric更多？
q_en: Which warehouse has more Cotton Fabric between the main and auxiliary warehouses?

command: SELECT id FROM materials WHERE name = 'Cotton Fabric';
SELECT id, name FROM warehouse WHERE name IN ('Main Warehouse', 'Auxiliary warehouse');
SELECT wm.warehouse_id, wm.left_number FROM warehouse_material wm WHERE wm.material_id = 'm1' AND wm.warehouse_id IN ('w1', 'w2');
